JQuery plugin for a very simple sliding gallery

usage:
	$('#container').simpleGallery();
	
you can pass an options object with these params:
	perPage - number of slides perPage (default: 2),
	scrollPerPage - number of slides to scroll perPage (default: 1),
	speed - how fast to scroll in ms (default: 200),
	rightButton - jQuery selector for the rightButton (default: #rightButton),
	leftButton - jQuery selector for the leftButton (default: #leftButton)
	
	
		
	